  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Slice the doner meat into thin strips and season with cumin, coriander powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "3. Grill the meat for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked to your liking.",
    "4. Meanwhile, grill the pita bread for 1-2 minutes per side, or until crispy and slightly charred.",
